{"tid":666896,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法改會檢討性罪行諮詢3個月　倡廢部分同性罪行   影女可能刑事？","createTime":"2018-05-16T09:30:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T13:18:42.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"612940f2bdd6fcda94669324706350eae00dcb80","tid":666896,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T09:30:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180516/s00001/11c96391ec9ae6b856fae684cbcbafd1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180516%2Fs00001%2F11c96391ec9ae6b856fae684cbcbafd1.jpg&h=238fe174&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法改會轄下性罪行檢討小組委員會發表諮詢文件，就改革涉及「雜項性罪行」的相關法律提出初步建議，包括亂倫、露體、窺淫、獸交、戀屍行為及意圖犯性罪行而作出的行為等， 亦建議廢除一些同性或關乎同性的現有罪行。諮詢期3個月。<br />\n<br />\n諮詢文件主要建議如下：<br />\n<br />\n─新訂一項窺淫罪，將未經同意下為了性目的而對另一人進行觀察或視像記錄（例如以照片、錄影帶或數碼影像形式）的行為刑事化；<br />\n<br />\n─廢除一些同性或關乎同性的現有罪行：意圖作出肛交而襲擊、促致他人作出同性肛交、男子與男子非私下作出的嚴重猥褻作為，以及促致男子與男子作出嚴重猥褻作為<br />\n<br />\n─新訂一項性露體罪，涵蓋以特定受害人為目標，而以涉及性的形式在私人或公眾地方暴露生殖器官行為<br />\n<br />\n─保留亂倫為特定罪行，但改革罪行元素。另外，香港社會應考慮什麼範圍涉及性的行為會構成亂倫，以及該罪行應否涵蓋領養父母<br />\n<br />\n─新訂一項對死人進行涉及性的行為罪<br />\n<br />\n─新訂一項為性目的而施用物質罪，以取代現有的施用藥物以獲得或便利作非法的性行為罪<br />\n<br />\n─新訂一項意圖犯性罪行而犯罪的罪行，以取代現有的意圖作出肛交而襲擊罪<br />\n<br />\n─新訂一項意圖犯性罪行而侵入罪，以取代現有的入屋犯法（意圖強姦）罪<br />\n<br />\n─現有的獸交罪應由與動物性交罪取代；<br />\n<br />\n性罪行檢討小組委員會主席鄧樂勤指，諮詢文件中各項建議旨在促進討論，不一定代表小組委員會最終結論。<br />\n<br />\n公眾人士可往香港中環下亞厘畢道18號律政中心東座4樓法律改革委員會秘書處，索取諮詢文件文本，亦可於法改會網站閱覽內容，<a href=\"http://網址是www.hkreform.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%B6%B2%E5%9D%80%E6%98%AFwww.hkreform.gov.hk&d=tHclZjdFv0JrE21jMsQuEAtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=60280ea0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">網址是www.hkreform.gov.hk</a>。所有意見須於8月15日或之前，以郵遞、傳真（3918 4096）或電郵（hklrc@hkreform.gov.hk）送達委員會秘書。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180516/s00001/1526458658167\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180516%2Fs00001%2F1526458658167&d=tHclZjdFv0JrE21jMsQuEAtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=98e3ea8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180516%2Fs00001%2F1526458658167&h=9237a352\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180516/s00001/1526458658167</a>"},{"pid":"c01fb6e9cbe4cc5d78975cfbc20a4e77343c3d84","tid":666896,"uid":108347,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T09:34:54.000Z","msg":"為了性目的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即係蘋果影女就話我登報姐，毒撚影就肯定係番屋企打飛機所以有罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664bfd1a3b6c9c8317457e9b44f2a5f17d3d8b30","tid":666896,"uid":35667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T09:37:25.000Z","msg":"窺淫罪係咪任佢up<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261c7209fbe97d5e1c306ffdcc5b2130ae18dee7","tid":666896,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c01fb6e9cbe4cc5d78975cfbc20a4e77343c3d84","tid":666896,"uid":108347,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T09:34:54.000Z","msg":"為了性目的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即係蘋果影女就話我登報姐，毒撚影就肯定係番屋企打飛機所以有罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T09:38:47.000Z","msg":"登報咪又係俾讀者打j"},{"pid":"c3799458d8743d9c03dff890104c1241734b03d8","tid":666896,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c01fb6e9cbe4cc5d78975cfbc20a4e77343c3d84","tid":666896,"uid":108347,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T09